Description:
   Verdict is the Sentinel's signature judgment strike. After observing and
   analyzing a target through the Pale Ledger's framework, the Sentinel
   delivers a decisive blow that represents the culmination of their
   assessment. Verdict deals enhanced damage based on how thoroughly the
   Sentinel has studied the target — if Read Opponent is active, the blow
   is significantly more powerful.

   Delivering a Verdict is a formal act in the Sentinel doctrine: it
   closes the observational cycle and resets the Sentinel's assessment of
   the opponent. The damage scales with combat intelligence gathered, making
   it most devastating against targets who have been extensively analyzed.
   The Sentinel should use Verdict as a finisher after setting up with
   Read Opponent and other debuffing techniques.
